    CS --> OVERLAY
    BG -->|"Badge update<br/>green/red/yellow"| BG

    POPUP --> TAB_SCAN
    POPUP --> TAB_UPLOAD
    TAB_SCAN -->|"GET_LAST_RESULT"| BG
    TAB_UPLOAD -->|"DETECT_ROW (per row)"| BG
